Structure:

	Controller gives data to view (output) / gets data back (input)
	Screen will be refreshed in the case of a data change (output)

public graphics: interaction and run application: setTroops(), getMap() ...
private data: real implementation: setTroops(), getMap ... every field in a seperate object
private field: background, troop, marked?
private OutputController: real implementation: drawMap()
private InputController: real implementation: getInput()...
